Mutual Credit Guarantee

Government of 
India, NCGTC 
• Provides 60% guarantee coverage for 
MSME loans up to ₹100 crore for 
equipment/machinery.  
• Minimum 75% of project cost must be for 
equipment/machinery.  
• Loan repayment: 8 years for loans up to ₹50 
crore with a 2-year moratorium.  
• Annual Guarantee Fee: Nil in the first year, 
1.5% for three years, 1% thereafter.  
• Supports Make in India and MSME 
manufacturing growth.
